        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "She was alone on this occasion, in one of the smaller of the numerous rooms devoted by mrs Touchett to social uses, and there was that in her expression and attitude which would have suggested that she was expecting a visitor.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_143879_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/143879/1926_143879_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "She wished rather to forestall his arrival by a process of conjecture, and to judge by the expression of her face this attempt gave her plenty to do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
