        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I learned that mrs Gardener had gone to Omaha to hear Booth and Barrett, who were to play there next week, and that Mary Anderson was having a great success in \"A Winter's Tale,\" in London.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
