        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Whenever she caught him slipping away from the cabin, she whipped him unmercifully, and told him what dreadful things old mr d'Arnault would do to him if he ever found him near the \"Big House.\" But the next time Samson had a chance, he ran away again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
