        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "In the middle of a crashing waltz d'Arnault suddenly began to play softly, and, turning to one of the men who stood behind him, whispered, \"Somebody dancing in there.\" He jerked his bullet head toward the dining room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
