        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Tiny looked alarmed. \"mrs Gardener would n't like it,\" she protested.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "\"She'd be awful mad if you was to come out here and dance with us.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Now, you're Lena, are you?--and you're Tony and you're Mary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Have I got you all straight?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "\"You'll wake the cook, and there'll be the devil to pay for me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "\"Oh, what do you care, Johnnie?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Come along, nobody'll tell tales.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Johnnie shook his head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "\"Oh, we'll make it all right with Molly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Get your back up, Johnnie.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000027_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000027_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "One of these city gentlemen, I bet! Now, you girls, you ain't goin' to let that floor get cold?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Mary Dusak was broad and brown of countenance, slightly marked by smallpox, but handsome for all that.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147979_000029_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147979/1926_147979_000029_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I walked home with Antonia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Since the scandal about the Swedish girl, Wick Cutter could never get his wife to stir out of Black Hawk without him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "The day after the Cutters left, Antonia came over to see us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Grandmother noticed that she seemed troubled and distracted.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I could n't sleep much last night.\" She hesitated, and then told us how strangely mr Cutter had behaved before he went away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "She would be perfectly safe, he said, as he had just put a new Yale lock on the front door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "She had n't liked the way he kept coming into the kitchen to instruct her, or the way he looked at her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "\"I feel as if he is up to some of his tricks again, and is going to try to scare me, somehow.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Antonia turned to me eagerly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I'd make up my bed nice and fresh for you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I was afraid to leave the window open last night.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I found that I slept there as well as anywhere, and when I got home in the morning, Tony had a good breakfast waiting for me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "The third night I spent at the Cutters', I awoke suddenly with the impression that I had heard a door open and shut.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "The next thing I knew, I felt some one sit down on the edge of the bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I was only half awake, but I decided that he might take the Cutters' silver, whoever he was.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I held my breath and lay absolutely still.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "A hand closed softly on my shoulder, and at the same moment I felt something hairy and cologne scented brushing my face.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I caught a handful of whiskers and pulled, shouting something.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Where is she, you nasty whelp, where is she?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Under the bed, are you, hussy?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "I know your tricks! Wait till I get at you!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "So long as Cutter had me by the throat, there was no chance for me at all. I got hold of his thumb and bent it back, until he let go with a yell.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "Her cry of fright awakened me. Truly, I was a battered object.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "My lip was cut and stood out like a snout.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "My nose looked like a big blue plum, and one eye was swollen shut and hideously discolored.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1926_147987_000014_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1926/147987/1926_147987_000014_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1926",
        "content": "She seemed to understand, though I was too faint and miserable to go into explanations.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
